    "long_instructions": "### Wakeup Song\r\n\r\n**Define:** You've been asked to design a new alarm clock ringtone that helps people wake up. The volume should slowly increase as different tracks play and end in some kind of big surprise.\r\n\r\n**Prepare:** Pick the tracks and effects you want to use and imagine what you want the timeline to look like. Consider using rests to surprise the listener!\r\n\r\n**Try:** Create your alarm clock ringtone!\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#ebe8f1; border: 0; border-radius: 10px; clear:both; padding: 5px\">\r\n\r\nNeed some help? Try the [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i> Docs](#clickable=documentation-button) in the upper-right corner!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n**Reflect:** In order to pass this level, make sure your code has:\r\n- At least 6 tracks\r\n- At least 3 effects\r\n- A \"rising\" volume and a surprise moment!",
    "display_name": "Time to Wake Up",
